OL,3,CMan dead and two people in hospital
OL,4,Cfollowing crash on A709 near Lochmaben
OL,6,FA man has died and two people are in
OL,7,Fhospital in a serious condition
OL,8,Ffollowing a crash on the A709.
OL,10,FPolice say the crash, which involved a
OL,11,Fblack Vauxhall Vectra and a white
OL,12,FCitroen Dispatch, happened at around
OL,13,F7.35pm on Saturday (June 6) on the
OL,14,FA709 Dumfries to Lockerbie road, near
OL,15,Fto Lochfield, Lochmaben.
OL,17,FThree people were taken to hospital,
OL,18,Fbut the driver of the Vauxhall, a 50-
OL,19,Fyear-old man, died shortly afterwards.
