OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1780942271
OL,3,CMan dead and two people in hospital
OL,4,Cfollowing crash on A709 near Lochmaben
OL,6,FThe people travelling in the Citroen,
OL,7,Fa 67-year-old man and a 55-year-old
OL,8,Fwoman, remain in hospital in a serious
OL,9,Fcondition.
OL,11,FSergeant Wayne Carnochan said: "Our
OL,12,Fthoughts are with the family of the
OL,13,Fman who has died at this time.
OL,15,F"Our enquiries are ongoing to
OL,16,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,17,Fthis crash and we are appealing to
OL,18,Fanyone who may have witnessed anything
OL,19,Faround this time to contact us.
OL,26,@sD@`OUwD@AOU
